PLACEHOLDER — replace this file with your real CV.

🔧 HOW TO REPLACE
1. Export your CV as a PDF.
2. Name it exactly: jobaedul-islam-jewel-cv.pdf
3. Drop it into the /public folder, replacing this file.

The "Download CV" buttons across the site link to /jobaedul-islam-jewel-cv.pdf,
so once you replace this file the buttons will serve your real document.

(If you prefer a different filename, update `resumeFile` in src/lib/site.ts.)
